{"tid":2493724,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"(初次獨遊記)6日5夜福岡小倉之旅","createTime":"2021-04-18T06:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T08:21:23.000Z","uid":116706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad14f80f5dd2a06b985f4c7dae1743c79ee62dde","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:34:53.000Z","msg":"呢排睇旅遊台, 見到經過呢一年時間武肺搞到冇得去旅行而令到遊記數目越嚟越少, 啱啱碌返之前第一次獨遊嘅相, 就心血來潮試下寫小弟第一篇遊記<br />\n(文筆唔好請諒解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n睇開旅遊台同blog, 見到其他人獨遊經歷好似好正, 無拘無束咁, 所以一路以嚟都好想試下. 喺2018年中, 由於我攞咗年尾一個禮拜大假, 所以就諗住嚟一次獨遊<br />\n<br />\n地點方面諗咗一陣, 由於之前旅遊經驗好少, 只係細個同屋企人去過大陸同台灣. 第一次去都係去返啲大路嘅日韓台泰算. 韓國一條仔去冇嘢好做, 台灣就去過. 日本泰國中間揀, 最後揀咗去好多香港人嘅鄉下-日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用咗幾個月時間做research睇blog, 最後終於喺2018年10月尾出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRmXGBz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRmXGBz.png&h=1769f811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sP4uxJQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsP4uxJQ.png&h=1853514e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AcsG8ha.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAcsG8ha.png&h=6bd502ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay1-2: 福岡巿內<br />\nDay3: 太宰府<br />\nDay4: 糸島<br />\nDay5: 門司港+下關<br />\nDay6: 小倉<br />\n<br />\n行程方面, 由於唔好行街, 所以主要都係睇景點. 洗費方面成程好似用咗4千蚊左右<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去住啲相先 (陳年舊手機影, 有啲會矇)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YFfhGL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYFfhGL4.jpg&h=a9b4c1ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZuDftqY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZuDftqY.jpg&h=de4ea024&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a1b46cJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa1b46cJ.jpg&h=7a07b51f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qyOOq0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qyOOq0.jpg&h=89931f4a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gmObMcJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgmObMcJ.jpg&h=09c9c33d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnV5QEo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnV5QEo.jpg&h=401f50f1&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVdK6cK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVdK6cK.jpg&h=6e406dd3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fRX4mL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfRX4mL4.jpg&h=f78bc445&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7pircH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7pircH.jpg&h=c2ef5eff&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XgERMcK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgERMcK.jpg&h=c023f6ba&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZgkExG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZgkExG.jpg&h=483679f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxQdZxF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxQdZxF.jpg&h=58f26792&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8HoCjo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8HoCjo.jpg&h=2640f1cc&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K6RgXjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK6RgXjp.jpg&h=9ad25108&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LDB8Oq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLDB8Oq4.jpg&h=84d97c33&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kptnSSJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkptnSSJ.jpg&h=a8e0e5f0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbXsjxz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbXsjxz.jpg&h=690c2afe&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EAzKmL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAzKmL1.jpg&h=9e73be64&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後不定時出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f4c1a7d1380686d92ccc26b98b021c14d6f2fc","tid":2493724,"uid":292601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"正 我都係同你差唔多<br />\n2015左右獨遊北九州<br />\n自始愛上左呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但應該再無機會獨遊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea24d71136a42b5e02f459a9e1b07d97caaaca6","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:24:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 1</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n飛機就搭UO, 早機去下午機返連稅1128. 呢個時間我又覺得OK喎. 再平啲時間又太閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nUO600 0735HKG-&gt;1200FUK<br />\n搭通宵機場巴士去機場, 5點幾去到. 用張已成歷史嘅AE CX elite入公廁lounge食咗個魚蛋粉坐多一陣就上機<br />\n<br />\n瞓咗陣就到福岡. 福岡機場嘅好處就係近巿區, 搭地鐵幾個字就到博多駅.<br />\n拿拿臨拖住篋去食嘢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtgMAeC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtgMAeC.jpg&h=72cd0859&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一雙見都多人推介, 喺博多駅行幾分鐘就到<br />\n去到見到有條廿幾人嘅人龍, 好似全部都係日本人? 之前聽講話去有人龍嘅鋪頭實無死<br />\n望一望入面得10幾個位, 結果由12點幾等咗個幾鐘去到兩點先入到去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BEMTZJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBEMTZJM.jpg&h=6472f5a0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n佢賣點係濃豬骨湯, 喺門口排緊隊嘅時候已經聞到一大浸其實有啲臭嘅味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似有啲生豬嘅腥味, 心諗今次可能伏咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但見到咁多人排隊, 就抱住一試無妨嘅心態試下<br />\n啊, 食落口又幾好味喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完拉麪就返酒店, 食飽飽最啱就行路<br />\n所以就拖住篋由博多行去天神南嘅酒店擺低行李先, 行到去啱啱夠鐘check in<br />\n今次book咗喺天神南嘅Benikea Calton Hotel Fukuoka Tenjin, 4晚唔使1200蚊, 好抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dZPFENy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdZPFENy.jpg&h=2c40f2d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhDOOHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhDOOHy.jpg&h=5b0eabf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A6RAtHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6RAtHC.jpg&h=d4e8d3e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvqtOH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvqtOH6.jpg&h=e3b08908&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n第一次用免治馬桶, 感覺好奇妙, 好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>待續</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"60923dbba32cd72237de0a3a8f05f7b3a572acdc","tid":2493724,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:25:36.000Z","msg":"牛腸鍋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23be1f4e7d39b24ebfc10f0b37f685261967312f","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:18:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">Day 1 (cont.)</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n擺低行李就拿拿臨出去. 由於Day1-2都喺福岡巿內, 而福岡地鐵又貫穿咗巿區好多景點, 所以喺福岡機場時就買咗地鐵2 day pass, 機場出巿區嗰程就用得 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vy2sjUy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVy2sjUy.jpg&h=65dbc4cd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n酒店行5分鐘就到地鐵站, 第一站筥崎宮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E5pRMA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE5pRMA8.jpg&h=7aef45f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sc2gdf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSc2gdf8.jpg&h=9d4dd3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKssjV8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKssjV8.jpg&h=75829980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MO5xv23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMO5xv23.jpg&h=01b9cc5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x0v18PK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0v18PK.jpg&h=d4e3194d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後搭返嚟東長寺, 櫛田神社<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQqNjXz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQqNjXz.jpg&h=070e4654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解鎖subway pass背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdOyZZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdOyZZg.jpg&h=5906a2b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8hVNjZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8hVNjZg.jpg&h=352edc9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijRwMEe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijRwMEe.jpg&h=238a9fad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iD1dfxA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiD1dfxA.jpg&h=173577d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vmMAxB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vmMAxB.jpg&h=9a40cc95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KXkhHcA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKXkhHcA.jpg&h=b6d51be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VSap6Eg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVSap6Eg.jpg&h=5824004d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DvmpqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8DvmpqW.jpg&h=ae40429d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eu2WXLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Feu2WXLW.jpg&h=9e0a3647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到隻牛畀人摸到令哂, 我又摸一摸先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M89eKr7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM89eKr7.jpg&h=618376bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日覺得日本文化源遠流長, 啲神社好值得去. 雖然好似間間差唔多, 但係入到去成個環境會令你心靈即刻洗滌咗, 舒服哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多本地人都會入去誠心參拜<br />\n<br />\n行到差唔多, 過隔離5分鐘路程嘅博多運河城行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmDWdnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmDWdnV.jpg&h=01b27df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFrpngu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFrpngu.jpg&h=554199b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2zuyn9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2zuyn9.jpg&h=63be1201&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n都係普通商場賣衫褲鞋襪, 唔多啱睇<br />\n5樓有個拉麵街, 但係夜晚已經鎖定咗食炸豬扒飯, 所以唔喺度食<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tabelog.com/fukuoka/A4001/A400103/40018942/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftabelog.com%2Ffukuoka%2FA4001%2FA400103%2F40018942%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RFQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=defce797\" target=\"_blank\">https://tabelog.com/fukuoka/A4001/A400103/40018942/</a><br />\n夜晚喺天神駅Solaria Stage嘅かつ心食, 而家Tabelog有 3.48分<br />\nSolaria Stage B2層全部都係食肆. 唔知係咪仲早(6點)所以唔太多人<br />\n<img src=\"https://tblg.k-img.com/restaurant/images/Rvw/82218/640x640_rect_82218242.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftblg.k-img.com%2Frestaurant%2Fimages%2FRvw%2F82218%2F640x640_rect_82218242.jpg&h=8d6df53e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖from tabelog<br />\n嗌咗個とんかつ膳(大)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EsLReh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EsLReh.jpg&h=d701dc28&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n炸得鬆脆又有汁, 幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飽飽行多陣商場就返酒店<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>Day 1 完</strong></ins>"},{"pid":"23b0ee6b5fceac45e2bc4391f9c875aa29fbf403","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f4c1a7d1380686d92ccc26b98b021c14d6f2fc","tid":2493724,"uid":292601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"正 我都係同你差唔多<br />\n2015左右獨遊北九州<br />\n自始愛上左呢個地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但應該再無機會獨遊了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:20:34.000Z","msg":"北九州夠靜又多地方行<br />\n<br />\n好掛住旅行嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd4535cc3f4b63928117cfe7063d01b93b40743","tid":2493724,"uid":116706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"<del>北</del>九州夠靜又多地方行"}]}